WEBVTT

01:42.080 --> 01:47.280
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL ZHU YU
BY TUAN ZI LAI XI ON JJWXC.NET

01:50.520 --> 01:53.960
MANUAL OF THE BEDCHAMBER ARTS

01:58.520 --> 01:59.480
I don't need this.

01:59.560 --> 02:01.400
He's hurt like that.
We won't be needing it.

02:01.480 --> 02:03.120
Soon enough, you will.

02:03.200 --> 02:04.080
Back to the bridal chamber.

02:05.160 --> 02:06.000
Go on.

02:07.600 --> 02:09.160
MARRIAGE

02:16.320 --> 02:17.200
Wait.

02:20.520 --> 02:21.680
Sorry.

02:28.640 --> 02:31.120
I'm used to living alone.
I keep forgetting there's a man here now.

02:36.040 --> 02:36.880
Come in.

02:49.200 --> 02:50.880
-Let me help.
-No need.

02:53.160 --> 02:54.040
I can manage.

02:54.120 --> 02:55.520
Manage what?

02:56.080 --> 02:57.360
You're impossible.

02:57.440 --> 02:59.520
Is it that hard
to let me help you with the medicine?

02:59.600 --> 03:01.720
These wounds keep reopening.

03:02.560 --> 03:05.000
Do you know how much that costs?
How much you're hurting yourself?

03:08.360 --> 03:09.720
Men and women shouldn't touch freely.

03:10.640 --> 03:12.760
What do you mean touch?

03:12.840 --> 03:14.880
The day Song Yan came making trouble,
didn't we already…

03:20.200 --> 03:21.040
touch?

03:23.720 --> 03:26.160
That wasn't that kind of touch.

03:29.000 --> 03:32.280
Then, when I carried you out of the snow,
that counted, didn't it?

03:36.000 --> 03:38.440
-It did.
-Then what's the difference?

03:44.200 --> 03:45.400
Relax.

03:45.480 --> 03:47.360
I don't have
any improper thoughts about you.

03:47.440 --> 03:49.000
With you covered in wounds like this,

03:49.080 --> 03:51.160
even if I did, what good would it do?

03:58.200 --> 04:01.520
Fan Changyu, why would you say that?

04:07.280 --> 04:08.200
This medicine doesn't…

04:09.280 --> 04:10.640
doesn't need that much.

04:12.400 --> 04:13.240
Too much?

04:14.920 --> 04:17.079
Mr. Zhao uses about this much.

04:21.360 --> 04:22.320
New medicine?

04:22.400 --> 04:23.480
Why didn't you tell me?

04:24.400 --> 04:25.480
It's fine.

04:26.080 --> 04:27.280
Just wrap it properly.

04:36.120 --> 04:39.800
These scars…
Are they from escorting caravans?

04:41.640 --> 04:44.480
I didn't even notice them
when I was changing your clothes.

04:45.120 --> 04:46.040
It's nothing.

04:46.840 --> 04:50.000
I kept you away because I didn't want
these scars to frighten you.

04:54.040 --> 04:55.840
Hold still. I'm almost done.

05:21.040 --> 05:23.240
Other escorts rely on skill.

05:24.160 --> 05:26.440
You rely on sheer stubborn luck.

05:30.880 --> 05:32.360
Don't risk your life like that again.

05:32.960 --> 05:34.000
Worst comes to worst,

05:34.920 --> 05:36.000
I'll work harder.

05:37.520 --> 05:38.680
Slaughter more pigs to feed you.

05:59.880 --> 06:01.600
I'll go sleep downstairs with Ning.

06:02.800 --> 06:03.920
No need.

06:04.000 --> 06:04.880
Later,

06:06.120 --> 06:07.200
I'll sleep in the main hall.

06:09.640 --> 06:10.480
All right.

06:12.080 --> 06:14.880
I'll bring you a basin of water.
Wipe yourself down.

06:19.720 --> 06:21.120
I'll take the wedding robe downstairs.

06:24.400 --> 06:25.840
MANUAL OF THE BEDCHAMBER ARTS

06:43.320 --> 06:45.160
Why are you hiding this sort of thing?

06:48.320 --> 06:51.400
-That's not--
-I thought you were resting properly.

06:51.480 --> 06:53.200
Who would have thought?

06:55.040 --> 06:56.800
I'll overlook it this time.

06:56.880 --> 06:59.160
I'll throw this filth away.
Don't look at it again.

07:07.000 --> 07:08.080
How mortifying!

07:14.760 --> 07:15.880
What's that?

07:17.960 --> 07:19.320
Get back.

07:19.920 --> 07:21.640
Careful. Don't get spotted.

07:28.520 --> 07:29.800
She's coming down.

08:03.040 --> 08:05.280
See? I told you.

08:05.360 --> 08:08.720
On their wedding night, sleeping apart.

08:08.800 --> 08:11.080
That live-in marriage has to be fake.

08:12.160 --> 08:14.480
Honey, you're smart.

08:14.560 --> 08:16.320
That wretched Fan Changyu

08:16.400 --> 08:18.240
thinks she can fool the authorities

08:18.320 --> 08:20.120
and keep the house for herself.

08:20.840 --> 08:21.920
Look more carefully.

08:22.760 --> 08:24.840
I am looking carefully.

08:26.320 --> 08:27.920
I told you to look inside carefully,

08:28.000 --> 08:29.120
not stare at that!

08:35.280 --> 08:36.520
Over there. Watch that side.

08:49.080 --> 08:50.480
Honey, hold on.

08:51.160 --> 08:53.120
She went back in with a basin of water.

08:53.200 --> 08:54.320
That's not sleeping apart.

08:54.400 --> 08:56.840
Don't rush it. Keep watching.

08:57.520 --> 08:58.360
What is it?

09:02.440 --> 09:04.840
My uncle and aunt are listening outside.

09:05.600 --> 09:07.240
They must suspect

09:07.320 --> 09:09.120
this marriage is only for show.

09:16.480 --> 09:17.680
Come here.

09:24.160 --> 09:26.440
Can I stay here for now?

09:27.160 --> 09:28.720
Slip upstairs later?

09:30.000 --> 09:31.160
Sleep here tonight.

09:34.160 --> 09:35.280
If you leave,

09:35.920 --> 09:37.120
people will start to doubt.

09:38.680 --> 09:39.640
Close the window.

09:41.040 --> 09:41.880
All right.

09:49.960 --> 09:51.320
What's going on?

09:51.400 --> 09:53.200
They've shut the window.

09:53.280 --> 09:54.400
That's not right.

09:55.000 --> 09:56.400
Overnight,

09:57.040 --> 09:58.720
she finds a man

09:58.800 --> 10:00.240
willing to marry into her house?

10:00.840 --> 10:02.000
Something's off.

10:10.800 --> 10:11.640
Give me the candle.

10:19.400 --> 10:20.240
Come closer.

10:37.840 --> 10:38.680
Turn around.

10:47.480 --> 10:48.440
Closer still.

10:57.360 --> 10:59.400
They're consummating the marriage.

10:59.480 --> 11:01.360
Consummating it right there,

11:01.440 --> 11:02.520
in the main hall!

11:07.240 --> 11:10.280
Your clothes are soaked through
with sweat.

11:10.360 --> 11:11.600
Go change into something dry.

11:19.880 --> 11:21.040
Take off my clothes.

12:22.000 --> 12:23.080
Help me lie down.

12:34.520 --> 12:35.560
Don't move.

12:39.960 --> 12:40.800
Honey, look.

12:40.880 --> 12:42.240
Just like the drawings in that book.

12:43.560 --> 12:44.960
Stop staring at that book!

12:46.680 --> 12:48.640
That shameless Fan Changyu.

13:24.480 --> 13:25.680
Blow out the candle.

13:32.080 --> 13:33.800
Honey, the light's gone.

13:33.880 --> 13:34.960
Nothing left to see.

13:35.040 --> 13:36.280
Let's go.

13:36.360 --> 13:37.440
Wait.

13:38.160 --> 13:39.440
I have a feeling

13:40.120 --> 13:41.400
this isn't what it looks like.

13:43.720 --> 13:45.040
Where are you going?

13:45.120 --> 13:46.480
I'll climb over again.

13:46.560 --> 13:47.680
Take a proper look.

13:57.080 --> 13:58.040
Damn stray cat!

13:58.120 --> 13:59.840
Back again stealing my meat?

14:01.280 --> 14:02.120
That's no cat.

14:02.720 --> 14:03.840
Who's out there?

14:10.760 --> 14:12.000
So it really is some beast.

14:12.080 --> 14:13.600
Shameless thing.

14:13.680 --> 14:14.880
Sneaking around at midnight
to steal from me.

14:14.960 --> 14:17.160
Don't let me catch you next time.
I won't spare you!

14:22.240 --> 14:25.320
Do you think she really consummated it?

14:26.960 --> 14:28.720
Then… Then we should leave.

14:28.800 --> 14:30.400
Or we'll be the ones laid out here.

14:31.200 --> 14:32.040
Quick, go.

15:03.920 --> 15:04.760
Much obliged.

15:29.920 --> 15:32.360
FAN'S PORK STALL

15:46.120 --> 15:47.920
-Just this piece?
-That one.

15:48.480 --> 15:50.280
See? Full weight.

15:50.360 --> 15:51.360
-Come again.
-Of course.

15:51.440 --> 15:52.680
Care for some braised pork?

15:52.760 --> 15:53.600
-That one.
-Pig ear.

15:55.280 --> 15:57.080
One jin. Here you go.

15:58.040 --> 15:58.840
Thank you.

15:58.920 --> 16:01.000
-Nice balance of fat and lean, isn't it?
-Perfect.

16:03.960 --> 16:04.680
Thank you, madam.

16:15.320 --> 16:16.360
Madam, some pork.

16:19.040 --> 16:19.880
Coming.

16:21.640 --> 16:22.800
Two jin?

16:22.880 --> 16:23.720
That'll do.

16:24.400 --> 16:26.360
PORK SHANK, PIG HEAD MEAT
SPICES, PORK BELLY

16:28.280 --> 16:29.520
Not bad at all.

16:29.600 --> 16:30.480
Sold out already.

16:30.560 --> 16:31.520
Mrs. Yin.

16:32.160 --> 16:33.400
Changyu.

16:33.480 --> 16:35.360
You've just married
and you're working already?

16:35.440 --> 16:36.600
You should take a break.

16:37.320 --> 16:38.640
Got to earn more silver.

16:38.720 --> 16:41.040
The sooner I rebuild my parents' pig pens,

16:41.120 --> 16:42.160
the better.

16:43.600 --> 16:46.480
True enough. Another mouth to feed now.

16:46.560 --> 16:47.680
You'll have to work harder.

16:50.080 --> 16:51.520
Your live-in husband…

16:51.600 --> 16:52.800
How was he last night?

16:53.520 --> 16:55.680
He's fine. Eats well, sleeps well.
His wounds are healing.

16:55.760 --> 16:57.280
That's not what I meant.

16:57.360 --> 17:00.120
Having children is no small matter.

17:00.680 --> 17:03.040
He's tall and broad-shouldered.

17:03.760 --> 17:05.200
Should be up to the task, right?

17:05.720 --> 17:08.040
-What are you saying?
-Look at you.

17:08.119 --> 17:10.040
I have no idea what you mean.

17:10.119 --> 17:11.800
-You know exactly what I mean.
-Keep moving.

17:11.880 --> 17:13.359
There are so many of them.

17:15.079 --> 17:16.440
They're arresting people again.

17:16.520 --> 17:18.480
What's happening?

17:21.200 --> 17:22.680
What now?

17:24.880 --> 17:26.440
What's happening?

17:27.079 --> 17:29.640
Rounding up refugees from Chongzhou again.

17:34.400 --> 17:37.040
Mrs. Yin, help me mind the stall.
I'll be back shortly.

17:38.640 --> 17:39.600
Where are you going?

17:41.960 --> 17:44.960
YAMEN

17:48.000 --> 17:48.880
All sorted.

17:48.960 --> 17:49.920
Keep it safe.

17:51.440 --> 17:52.360
Thank you, Mr. Wang.

17:53.840 --> 17:54.680
Come here a moment.

17:59.600 --> 18:00.440
What is it?

18:02.000 --> 18:04.760
-This is something for your trouble.
-What trouble?

18:05.520 --> 18:07.040
You're lawfully married.

18:07.120 --> 18:08.600
There's nothing improper here.

18:09.560 --> 18:11.440
Don't treat me like a stranger.

18:14.200 --> 18:16.080
-Thank you, Mr. Wang.
-Think nothing of it.

18:16.160 --> 18:18.080
It's cold. Go on home.

18:24.200 --> 18:26.760
LUO'S PAWNSHOP

18:29.360 --> 18:33.320
LUO'S PAWNSHOP

18:34.040 --> 18:35.120
Sold. Already sold.

18:35.200 --> 18:36.160
You sold it?

18:37.160 --> 18:38.440
How could you sell it?

18:39.040 --> 18:40.400
I pawned it as a live pledge.

18:40.480 --> 18:41.600
Look at the pawn ticket.

18:42.840 --> 18:44.440
It is a live pledge.

18:44.520 --> 18:46.640
But it clearly states,

18:47.240 --> 18:49.600
"If not redeemed within ten days,
it converts to forfeiture."

18:49.680 --> 18:52.760
See here. Your thumbprint.

18:53.440 --> 18:55.280
Who could even see that tiny line?

18:56.160 --> 18:57.880
And even if I saw it, I couldn't read!

18:59.200 --> 19:01.840
Mrs. Fan, if you pawn goods,

19:01.920 --> 19:03.680
must I also teach you your letters?

19:04.840 --> 19:06.000
You tricked me!

19:07.000 --> 19:09.400
We followed the contract exactly.

19:10.080 --> 19:11.320
Strange thing.

19:11.400 --> 19:12.560
It's a plain silver hairpin.

19:12.640 --> 19:14.800
That young gentleman wanted it.
Now you want it back.

19:14.880 --> 19:16.000
What's so special about it?

19:16.080 --> 19:17.640
What young gentleman? Where did he go?

19:18.680 --> 19:20.920
-Customer matters are not for--
-Tell me!

19:27.160 --> 19:28.280
It was the only thing

19:29.000 --> 19:30.520
my parents left me.

19:33.520 --> 19:36.640
Just a young man.
I truly do not know who he was.

19:37.440 --> 19:38.280
How much did you sell it for?

19:40.240 --> 19:41.160
Twenty taels.

19:42.960 --> 19:44.360
You sold it

19:44.440 --> 19:45.600
simply because he offered more?

19:47.640 --> 19:49.400
We have the pawn ticket as proof.

19:49.480 --> 19:53.440
Take it to the county yamen if you like.
I'm not afraid.

20:24.280 --> 20:26.640
Changyu. What are you doing here?

20:28.840 --> 20:30.040
What's gotten into her today?

20:30.800 --> 20:32.120
No idea.

20:44.800 --> 20:45.640
Changyu.

21:00.880 --> 21:04.800
Father. The sugar I hid got eaten by ants.

21:05.880 --> 21:07.440
All right, stop crying.

21:07.520 --> 21:09.240
I've got a plan.

21:13.920 --> 21:15.200
Look.

21:16.600 --> 21:18.000
Now the ants can't reach it.

21:18.720 --> 21:20.320
Father, you're amazing.

21:20.400 --> 21:23.560
Can you hide the rest for me too?

21:25.560 --> 21:27.080
You little fox.

21:27.160 --> 21:28.720
I knew you still had more stashed away.

21:29.320 --> 21:30.800
Don't tell your mother.

21:30.880 --> 21:32.640
She'll scold both of us.

21:32.720 --> 21:34.200
I won't, Father.

21:36.120 --> 21:37.600
Go pull me a blade of grass.

21:41.760 --> 21:42.680
Here.

21:46.080 --> 21:47.120
That way,

21:48.160 --> 21:49.480
we won't forget where it is.

21:49.560 --> 21:51.400
Father, you're the best.

21:51.480 --> 21:52.360
Look at you.

21:55.680 --> 21:56.720
Remember this.

21:56.800 --> 21:58.560
Every hurdle can be crossed.

21:59.160 --> 22:00.240
Tears may fall,

22:00.320 --> 22:01.920
but life goes on.

22:02.000 --> 22:04.240
If the sky collapses,
someone taller will hold it up.

22:04.320 --> 22:06.880
No matter what happens,
we eat well and sleep well.

22:06.960 --> 22:07.800
Yes, Father.

22:08.800 --> 22:09.800
Good girl.

22:38.320 --> 22:40.000
Thank you.

22:40.080 --> 22:42.400
Much obliged. Until next time.

22:42.480 --> 22:43.600
Until next time.

22:43.680 --> 22:44.560
I'm off.

22:46.280 --> 22:47.600
Careful there.

22:47.680 --> 22:49.000
Madam Song.

22:49.880 --> 22:50.800
Madam Song.

22:50.880 --> 22:53.600
Moving into a big house in the city now?

22:53.680 --> 22:55.120
What fortune.

22:55.800 --> 22:57.480
The magistrate favors us.

22:57.560 --> 22:59.760
My Yan has done well.

22:59.840 --> 23:02.240
Next year, he may even place first
in all three exams.

23:02.320 --> 23:04.320
Bring glory to our town.

23:04.400 --> 23:06.080
He will surely pass.

23:06.160 --> 23:08.840
Then I'll take your blessing to heart.

23:11.280 --> 23:12.480
Madam Song,

23:12.560 --> 23:15.920
Song Yan is about to become

23:16.000 --> 23:18.480
the magistrate's son-in-law.

23:19.520 --> 23:22.800
That promise you made about
my eldest grandson, lifting his labor duty

23:23.400 --> 23:25.760
and arranging a yamen post for him,

23:25.840 --> 23:27.160
when will that be fulfilled?

23:30.360 --> 23:33.800
And the matter of spreading word
that Fan Changyu is a calamity star,

23:33.880 --> 23:36.600
I made sure the whole village heard it.

23:36.680 --> 23:37.720
Absurd.

23:37.800 --> 23:39.200
When did I ever ask you?

23:41.000 --> 23:44.040
No, no, I meant nothing.

23:44.720 --> 23:46.200
You may rest assured.

23:46.280 --> 23:47.360
When the chance comes,

23:47.440 --> 23:49.600
I'll have Yan speak to the magistrate.

23:50.280 --> 23:51.160
Good, good.

23:52.520 --> 23:53.480
Fan Changyu, wait.

23:55.920 --> 23:56.960
Stand right there!

23:58.760 --> 24:01.080
Every hurdle can be crossed.

24:01.160 --> 24:03.640
If the sky collapses,
someone taller will hold it up.

24:10.600 --> 24:13.640
We've been neighbors for years.
Who knows when we'll meet again.

24:14.640 --> 24:16.160
This is a small token.

24:16.760 --> 24:18.160
Please accept it.

24:18.240 --> 24:21.320
And return the betrothal letter.

24:22.120 --> 24:23.000
Indeed.

24:23.080 --> 24:25.080
You've already taken a husband.

24:25.160 --> 24:27.280
Why keep that letter?

24:31.640 --> 24:32.480
That's it?

24:34.160 --> 24:36.640
How much do you claim our family owes you?

24:36.720 --> 24:39.080
And when did this even happen?

24:39.160 --> 24:40.560
Who witnessed it?

24:41.160 --> 24:42.000
Exactly.

24:42.080 --> 24:43.720
With no proof, who would believe you?

24:43.800 --> 24:46.360
If they truly owed you,

24:46.440 --> 24:48.400
wouldn't you have pressed them years ago?

24:48.480 --> 24:51.080
Who shows charity for over a decade

24:51.160 --> 24:53.240
without expecting repayment?

24:53.320 --> 24:55.360
You'd be a living bodhisattva.

25:03.120 --> 25:04.720
Enough.

25:05.960 --> 25:08.320
Take the silver. It should cover it.

25:08.400 --> 25:09.840
Return the letter.

25:16.680 --> 25:18.440
Look at her.

25:18.520 --> 25:20.480
Even this much is not enough.

25:20.560 --> 25:22.360
Fan Changyu.

25:22.440 --> 25:23.840
Greedy to the bone.

25:24.480 --> 25:25.960
You'd sell your soul for a coin.

25:26.040 --> 25:27.680
Unbelievable.

25:29.840 --> 25:31.960
Make way. Make way, please.

25:32.040 --> 25:33.600
You're all bullying my sister.

25:33.680 --> 25:35.680
My brother-in-law is here to back her up.

25:41.920 --> 25:42.760
Who's that?

25:42.840 --> 25:44.720
That's Changyu's husband.

25:44.800 --> 25:46.000
Him?

25:46.080 --> 25:47.240
And he's lame?

25:50.120 --> 25:52.280
Your wounds are still fresh.
You can hardly walk.

25:52.360 --> 25:54.040
How can you go running off with her?

25:54.760 --> 25:55.600
It's nothing.

25:58.280 --> 25:59.760
Even injured,

26:00.840 --> 26:03.120
I can still come take my wife home.

26:06.600 --> 26:09.680
This is between the Songs and the Fans.
What concern is it of yours?

26:10.200 --> 26:11.640
I bear the Fan name now.

26:12.720 --> 26:13.880
You want proof of debt?

26:14.400 --> 26:15.240
Very well.

26:15.840 --> 26:18.080
Let's settle the Songs' account
with the Fans first

26:18.600 --> 26:20.000
before you move away.

26:21.600 --> 26:23.840
One coffin, six taels and twenty mace.

26:24.440 --> 26:26.640
Twelve chi of fine cloth,
one tael and ten mace.

26:27.200 --> 26:29.760
Thirty baskets of eggs,
one tael and fifty mace.

26:31.160 --> 26:33.920
Three years of tuition,
nine taels and sixty mace.

26:35.680 --> 26:37.360
That broke scholar Song Yan studied

26:38.040 --> 26:40.760
only because the Fans supported him.

26:41.480 --> 26:44.480
And once he passed the provincial exam,

26:45.120 --> 26:47.200
before Erniu and Lihua
were even laid to rest,

26:47.280 --> 26:49.320
he forced Changyu
to cancel the engagement.

26:50.120 --> 26:51.520
Even Madam Song's food and clothing

26:51.600 --> 26:53.360
came from the Fan household.

26:53.440 --> 26:54.960
-Where did they find the nerve?
-Exactly.

26:59.320 --> 27:02.040
Mr. Zhao, what were the expenses?

27:02.120 --> 27:04.600
Three years of tuition
for that ungrateful Song Yan.

27:05.200 --> 27:07.080
Three taels and twenty mace a year.

27:08.120 --> 27:10.600
You figure out what that comes to
in three years.

27:10.680 --> 27:12.280
Nine taels and sixty mace in total.

27:12.880 --> 27:13.960
Not a small sum.

27:14.040 --> 27:16.040
And the pork
he collected during festivals.

27:16.120 --> 27:17.920
At least 20 cuts.

27:18.000 --> 27:19.960
Over two taels' worth.

27:20.040 --> 27:22.640
And when he fell ill the year before last,

27:22.720 --> 27:25.080
the medicine alone cost over one tael.

27:25.160 --> 27:26.640
Fan Erniu paid it.

27:26.720 --> 27:29.280
Never even told Lihua or Changyu.

27:29.360 --> 27:30.800
It only makes you angrier.

27:30.880 --> 27:32.280
Even the woman's monthly…

27:38.200 --> 27:40.520
Four bundles of bamboo baskets.
Thirty bundles of firewood.

27:40.600 --> 27:41.680
Five barrels of lamp oil.

27:41.760 --> 27:42.720
Three copper basins.

27:43.560 --> 27:44.440
One bamboo mat.

27:44.520 --> 27:45.600
And…

27:46.600 --> 27:48.280
Mind the ditch, Ning. Come back.

27:50.640 --> 27:53.160
Four bundles of menstrual cloth.

27:54.480 --> 27:56.400
-Menstrual cloth?
-They borrowed that too?

27:56.480 --> 27:58.680
And last Dragon Boat Festival,

27:58.760 --> 28:00.200
Madam Song visited us

28:00.280 --> 28:03.400
and left with a braised pig tail.

28:05.480 --> 28:06.880
Add it all together,

28:06.960 --> 28:07.920
the Fan family

28:08.000 --> 28:10.560
practically raised Madam Song and her son!

28:11.160 --> 28:13.520
Kang, how much did you gain

28:13.600 --> 28:15.640
from defending the Song family
so fiercely?

28:15.720 --> 28:17.200
Don't slander me.

28:17.280 --> 28:18.960
I took nothing.

28:19.040 --> 28:20.360
I'm just like everyone else here.

28:20.440 --> 28:22.280
I'm just passing by.

28:22.360 --> 28:24.520
I took nothing. Honestly.

28:25.280 --> 28:26.680
I'm just passing by.

28:27.200 --> 28:28.520
You, a grown man,

28:28.600 --> 28:31.000
speaking so freely
of women's private matters.

28:31.080 --> 28:33.120
You have no shame!

28:34.160 --> 28:36.400
Menstruation is the root of life.
The source of all mothers.

28:37.000 --> 28:38.400
Why should it not be spoken of?

28:39.080 --> 28:40.800
You may not speak of it,

28:40.880 --> 28:42.680
but you were quick enough to take it.

28:42.760 --> 28:44.920
Yes, and by the bundle.

28:45.000 --> 28:46.560
If it lasts half a month each time,

28:46.640 --> 28:48.080
perhaps you should see a physician!

28:48.160 --> 28:50.000
Go see one.

28:50.800 --> 28:51.880
Mind your own business!

28:52.400 --> 28:53.440
Stop laughing!

28:53.520 --> 28:54.520
Go get yourself treated!

28:54.600 --> 28:55.720
What business is it of yours?

28:56.280 --> 28:57.160
What's so funny?

28:57.240 --> 28:58.560
Mind your own business!

28:58.640 --> 29:00.480
Ladies, please refrain from harsh words.

29:02.360 --> 29:04.000
You underestimate
Mr. and Mrs. Fan's kindness

29:04.080 --> 29:05.320
toward me.

29:06.080 --> 29:08.280
They have passed on.
They deserve no further gossip.

29:09.320 --> 29:10.160
Changyu,

29:11.240 --> 29:13.280
though you speak harshly to me,

29:13.920 --> 29:15.000
I do not blame you.

29:16.640 --> 29:18.840
I understand your hasty marriage

29:19.440 --> 29:20.680
is in part because of me.

29:22.680 --> 29:23.720
From now on,

29:23.800 --> 29:25.680
you go your way, I'll go mine.

29:26.680 --> 29:27.800
But if you ever face hardship,

29:29.000 --> 29:30.800
send word to my residence.

29:31.640 --> 29:33.960
-I will always be your friend.
-Pah!

29:34.840 --> 29:36.520
Spare me your noble posturing.

29:37.120 --> 29:38.520
If not for me,

29:39.080 --> 29:41.040
would my parents have treated you so well?

29:42.240 --> 29:45.280
It's my own fault.
I was blind and foolish,

29:46.320 --> 29:48.760
unlucky enough to fall for a snake
in scholar's robes.

29:48.840 --> 29:51.400
-You…
-Repay the money. Now!

29:52.280 --> 29:56.640
-Yes, repay it.
-Repay what you owe!

29:56.720 --> 29:57.560
Very well.

29:57.640 --> 29:58.600
You owe it, you pay it.

29:58.680 --> 30:00.560
When gentlemen part,
they do not trade insults.

30:01.760 --> 30:02.680
I will repay.

30:05.040 --> 30:06.680
Round it off. 30 taels in total.

30:07.400 --> 30:09.040
If you doubt me, do the sums yourself.

30:12.880 --> 30:14.880
Mother. Pay her.

30:18.720 --> 30:20.320
We don't have that much silver.

30:23.160 --> 30:24.120
If it's short,

30:24.200 --> 30:25.640
write a note of debt.

30:27.320 --> 30:28.520
There's no brush or ink here.

30:29.360 --> 30:32.240
-I'll send it once we're in the city.
-No need.

30:32.800 --> 30:34.600
Bite your finger

30:34.680 --> 30:35.880
and press a thumbprint.

30:36.680 --> 30:37.920
Yes, press your thumb.

30:38.000 --> 30:40.160
-Press your thumb.
-Hurry.

30:40.240 --> 30:42.720
Absolutely not. Don't listen to them.

30:43.480 --> 30:44.320
We can…

30:44.920 --> 30:46.400
-You mustn't!
-Hold.

31:02.480 --> 31:04.480
It's only a few dozen taels.
I'll settle it for him.

31:04.560 --> 31:05.400
DAUGHTER OF MAGISTRATE CUI

31:09.120 --> 31:10.240
Ms. Cui.

31:10.320 --> 31:13.480
How could we trouble you
to grace this humble place?

31:14.560 --> 31:17.200
Song Yan is my father's student.

31:17.280 --> 31:19.400
Helping him is only proper.

31:21.120 --> 31:23.080
A scholar of the imperial court

31:23.160 --> 31:24.520
should not be haggled over

31:24.600 --> 31:26.400
by someone who reeks of copper coins.

31:39.360 --> 31:41.640
Some people are born to fortune.

31:42.280 --> 31:43.120
Like me.

31:43.840 --> 31:46.120
My father named me Qianjin.
A thousand pieces of gold.

31:46.200 --> 31:48.280
It was decided from birth
that I would never lack silver,

31:48.360 --> 31:49.520
with servants at my call.

31:50.600 --> 31:53.800
Others are born to misfortune.

31:54.400 --> 31:55.240
Like you.

31:55.920 --> 31:57.520
Orphaned young.

31:57.600 --> 31:58.720
With no one to rely on.

31:59.440 --> 32:01.040
Jade may be pretty,

32:01.120 --> 32:03.280
but it will never match gold for value.

32:03.360 --> 32:04.920
Here. 50 taels.

32:05.520 --> 32:06.440
Pick it up.

32:18.880 --> 32:19.720
That's enough, Changning.

32:20.400 --> 32:21.280
We don't take what's not ours.

32:22.600 --> 32:25.440
The betrothal letter was left beneath
the stone outside your gate long ago.

32:26.840 --> 32:27.680
Mother.

32:28.800 --> 32:30.160
It ended between us long ago.

32:31.760 --> 32:34.240
That extra silver covers the interest.

32:34.320 --> 32:36.040
After all, your pride

32:36.760 --> 32:37.880
isn't worth much.

32:38.400 --> 32:40.040
What is owed to me, I will take.

32:40.120 --> 32:41.520
What is not, I will not.

32:41.600 --> 32:42.440
And besides,

32:43.840 --> 32:45.040
he isn't worth much.

32:47.720 --> 32:49.880
Wait. I'm not done.

32:49.960 --> 32:51.400
-Come back! How rude.
-Yan.

32:51.480 --> 32:53.000
Yan, help me lift it.

32:53.080 --> 32:54.160
Quickly.

32:56.000 --> 32:58.320
Whoever helps
gets the silver on the ground.

33:12.680 --> 33:13.520
All right. Come on.

33:16.440 --> 33:17.280
Finally.

33:21.000 --> 33:22.160
Finally found it.

33:24.120 --> 33:24.960
I'll rip it.

33:30.080 --> 33:32.000
Ning, go home with Zheng.

33:54.120 --> 33:55.240
He's only a provincial graduate.

33:56.200 --> 33:58.120
Across the capital and 17 prefectures,

33:58.200 --> 33:59.360
how many graduates are made each year?

34:00.040 --> 34:01.640
What is one Song Yan?

34:05.600 --> 34:06.960
If you must say such things,

34:07.040 --> 34:08.679
say them only in front of me.

34:09.480 --> 34:10.880
Not before others.

34:11.440 --> 34:12.560
They will laugh.

34:12.639 --> 34:13.639
Laugh?

34:15.120 --> 34:15.960
What would they laugh at?

34:16.639 --> 34:18.000
They would laugh

34:18.080 --> 34:19.880
that you hold no degree at all.

34:25.239 --> 34:27.920
I know you're trying to comfort me.

34:30.159 --> 34:31.040
I'm not.

34:31.120 --> 34:32.800
A provincial graduate?

34:32.880 --> 34:33.920
Even a palace graduate

34:34.600 --> 34:35.639
is nothing special.

34:38.840 --> 34:40.679
Look at you acting like a grand official.

34:42.120 --> 34:43.800
-I…
-You're smart.

34:44.480 --> 34:45.679
You've got nice handwriting.

34:46.400 --> 34:48.679
Why not study and sit
for the examinations?

34:48.760 --> 34:50.560
If you pass,

34:50.639 --> 34:52.080
you could hold office.

34:52.800 --> 34:54.280
My ambitions do not lie in court.

34:57.480 --> 34:58.880
That's a pity.

34:58.960 --> 35:02.160
I was hoping you'd become
some grand official

35:02.240 --> 35:04.520
and find a way to trip up Song Yan.

35:07.880 --> 35:09.080
All right.

35:13.720 --> 35:14.560
What is it?

35:18.720 --> 35:20.120
I'm not upset

35:21.520 --> 35:22.800
over Song Yan.

35:24.800 --> 35:26.720
It's my mother's hairpin. I lost it.

35:39.440 --> 35:43.000
-That hairpin--
-I've failed my parents.

35:43.080 --> 35:45.120
I pawned it as a live pledge.

35:45.720 --> 35:47.560
Wouldn't you know it,

35:47.640 --> 35:49.840
the crooked pawnbroker
sold it to some half-wit.

35:49.920 --> 35:52.840
That ridiculous man paid 20 taels for it.

35:52.920 --> 35:53.840
Twenty taels!

35:54.600 --> 35:56.040
With that kind of silver,

35:56.120 --> 35:57.840
I could carve out three of him.

35:59.560 --> 36:01.960
Some people seem to live
just to make others miserable.

36:14.520 --> 36:16.280
How did you get this?

36:16.360 --> 36:17.200
That buyer…

36:21.520 --> 36:23.360
You were the one who paid 20 taels?

36:26.000 --> 36:27.480
In a manner of speaking.

36:32.200 --> 36:33.360
I got you back.

36:38.640 --> 36:39.480
Wait.

36:40.120 --> 36:41.360
That crooked shopkeeper

36:42.040 --> 36:44.400
cheated you out of 20 taels!

36:45.000 --> 36:46.120
I'll get the money back.

36:51.600 --> 36:52.840
In truth, the buyer

36:54.320 --> 36:55.760
is the owner of a bookshop.

36:56.880 --> 36:58.880
He bought the hairpin for 20 taels.

37:01.480 --> 37:02.960
He appreciated my essays.

37:03.040 --> 37:06.320
When he sent silver as reward,

37:06.400 --> 37:07.760
he returned this hairpin as well.

37:08.440 --> 37:09.400
That's quite a coincidence.

37:11.160 --> 37:12.160
Indeed.

37:16.840 --> 37:17.720
Here is the silver.

37:23.600 --> 37:26.360
You earned that much from essays?

37:26.960 --> 37:28.960
Yes. Mr. Zhao can confirm.

37:29.640 --> 37:30.720
Where is this bookshop?

37:31.560 --> 37:32.680
I'll return the silver to him.

37:32.760 --> 37:33.640
No need.

37:34.400 --> 37:37.520
He is wealthy.
Twenty taels means little to him.

37:38.120 --> 37:39.520
At least I should thank him.

37:41.240 --> 37:42.160
Naturally.

37:43.240 --> 37:45.880
Once my injuries are healed,

37:45.960 --> 37:47.040
I'll take you to call on him.

37:48.800 --> 37:49.640
All right.

37:53.240 --> 37:54.440
Still,

37:54.520 --> 37:56.840
you need not sell essays
to support the household.

37:58.920 --> 37:59.840
I told you.

38:01.240 --> 38:02.520
I can slaughter pigs and feed you.

38:25.800 --> 38:26.840
SPIRIT TABLET OF MENG LIHUA
SPIRIT TABLET OF FAN ERNIU

38:26.920 --> 38:27.960
Mother,

38:28.040 --> 38:29.400
I've found the hairpin.

38:30.600 --> 38:33.520
All this time, I was afraid.
Afraid I'd done wrong.

38:35.280 --> 38:37.960
Afraid you would disapprove.
Afraid you'd be upset.

38:39.520 --> 38:42.640
Now that it has come back to me,

38:43.960 --> 38:46.480
it must be you watching over us.

38:49.120 --> 38:50.720
Only then can I set my heart at ease.

39:07.000 --> 39:08.080
Let me help you.

40:18.680 --> 40:24.120
HEJIAN LUYUAN ACADEMY

40:50.760 --> 40:52.320
An, I've got a chicken drumstick here.

40:52.400 --> 40:53.480
Care for a bite?

40:55.040 --> 40:55.880
I…

40:57.400 --> 40:58.480
I do not eat drumsticks.

40:58.560 --> 40:59.760
I've got a big one.

40:59.840 --> 41:01.000
Look at this.

41:03.160 --> 41:04.640
That is highly inappropriate.

41:04.720 --> 41:07.360
This is a hall of refined learning.
How can you sit here gnawing on meat?

41:07.960 --> 41:09.320
What if the headmaster sees?

41:54.760 --> 41:55.800
You foolish bird.

41:55.880 --> 41:57.600
Every time you arrive, you lose your way.

42:02.760 --> 42:03.960
All right, all right.

42:04.040 --> 42:05.800
Wait here. I'll return shortly.

42:08.200 --> 42:10.160
Today's copying punishment
is deemed complete.

42:10.240 --> 42:11.480
You may all return.

42:13.200 --> 42:14.440
Many thanks, Headmaster.

42:14.520 --> 42:16.520
An, thank the headmaster.

42:17.440 --> 42:19.480
Many thanks, Headmaster Gongsun.

42:26.520 --> 42:28.280
Recovering from injury
at the Fan house in Lin'an.

42:29.480 --> 42:32.120
Bring my registration and travel papers.

42:40.240 --> 42:42.000
You rogue, Xie Jiuheng.

42:42.080 --> 42:44.200
I knew you would not fall so easily.

45:23.400 --> 45:26.920
‎NO ANIMALS WERE HARMED
‎IN THE MAKING OF THIS EPISODE

45:27.000 --> 45:27.920
Subtitle translation by: Jiaxin Wang
